input_str: It seems that just about everyone is talking about the Kony 2012 video that's received more than 70 million views since it was posted last week. It's part of a campaign by the non-profit group Invisible Children to bring awareness to the evil deeds of rebel leader Joseph Kony who's Lord's Resistance Army (LRA) has been terrorizing Ugandans and people in Congo, the Central African Republic and South Sudan since the 1980s.
